\id 3JN Tutsa: Bible Translation 1st Edition
\h 3 Joon
\toc1 JOON ih Takjom raang arah Le
\toc2 3 Joon
\toc3 3Jn
\mt1 JOON
\mt2 Ih Takjom Raang Arah Le
\imt1 Ephangjatjih
\ip \bk Joon leeraang \bk* “mihak phokhoh” loong ih chaas phansiitte Gaius suh raang arah. Arah raangte ih Gaius ah phoongpha ha mamah liidih heh ih Kristaan wahoh loong ah nong sokboita. Erah damdi Diotrephes ngeh liiha mina dowa banban ih tong an ngeh baat rumha.
\iot Hemong Dowa Jatjih
\io1 Ephangjatjih (1-4)
\io1 Gaius ah phoongphaata (5-8)
\io1 Diotrephes ah dut haatta (9-10)
\io1 Demetrius suh baatta (11-12)
\io1 Hethoon (13-15)
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Esm 19:29; Rom 16:23; 1Kr 1:14\x* Mihak phokhoh taangnawa—
\p Ngah ih nga mongnook Gaius amiimiisak minchan hang asuh raanghang.
\p 
\v 2 Nga mongnook joonwah, ngah ih rangsoom hang, an damdoh ese toom ang ah eno sakse hanme toomtong uh ngeh ah—mamah liidih ngah ih ejat ehala an chiiala lam ni ese.
\v 3 Kristaan mina thok rum haano baat rum tahang an amiisak tiit asuh kamkam eh tuungmaanglu—saarookwe amiisak ni kamkam ih tonglu ah chaat angno ngah rapne roonlang.
\v 4 Tim chaat ang di uh emah than tah thaak roonkang, ngaasuh ngaasah amiisak ni tongla chaat angno roonlang thanthan ah.
\s1 Gaius phoongpha
\p 
\v 5 Nga mongnook joonwah, neng loong wenwah ang rum abah uh Kristaan loong raangtaan ih molu ah rapne tuungmaang theng reelu.
\v 6 Neng ih chaas mina loong asuh an minchan tiit ah baat rumha. Neng lakhoom raangtaan ih nong sokboi we an, erah doba Rangte tenroon thuktheng adoh khoom rum ah.
\v 7 Mamah liidih neng loong ah Kristo mootkaat raangtaan ih ejen dokchap erumta, neng ih lah hanpiite loong taangnawa huinong hui suh tah jam rumka.
\v 8 Seng Kristaan loong ah juuba neng loong ah chosok theng jaatjaat, enooba amiisak mootkaat raangtaan ih seng nong kattheng ang ah.
\s1 Diotrephes nyia Demetrius
\p 
\v 9 Ngah ih ethoosah chaas raangtaan ih le raanghang; enoothong neng lamsiitte likhiik angla Diotrephes rah ih, arah jenglang asuh hethung hetak nak toom koh ah.
\v 10 Ngah maatok doh wang hang, erah doh heh ih timjih reeta erah baat wanhang: Marah echoh theng baat tahe nyia eleek tiit baat tahe erah loong ah! Enoothong heh suh erah tah changka ang ah; heh ih Kristaan loong heh ih tah banpoon rumka ang ah, erah damdi marah mina ih Kristaan mina banpoon suh taat liiha suh uh heh ih etangpang erum ah, eno neng loong ah chaas nawa edok phanhaat esuh thun rum ah!
\p 
\v 11 Nga mongnook joonte, ethih ah nak nyoot uh, enoothong marah ese ah erah nyoot uh. Ngo ih ese re ah erah Rangte mina; ngo ih ethih reela erah ih Rangte ah tup muh.
\p 
\v 12 Thoontang ih Demetrius ese li rumha; amiisak tiitkhaap rah ih heh tiit ah naririh ih baat ha. Eno erah seng roidong tiitkhaap tim baat hi eradi wakbaat hi, an ih ejat ehu seng ih tim baat hi erah amiisak kabaat ih.
\s1 Jengseera jengkhaap
\p 
\v 13 Ngah ih sen suh baat theng hantek je ah, enoothong roong nyi leeraang nawa ih raang suh tah thunghaan kang.
\v 14 Nga tuungmaang eje ang lang sen damdoh elaang ih chomui suh ah, eno erah doh seng pupuh damdoh chomui ino ma roongwaan ih.
\p 
\v 15 Semroongroong ah sen damdoh toom angha.
\p Sen joonte loong ih jengse raajeng halan. Seng joonte loong ih waru waru ih jengse raajeng halan.
